# Deployment Guidelines

- The application is deployed on Google Cloud Run
- Always dockerize the application using the provided Dockerfile
- Push Docker images to Google Container Registry (GCR) for deployment
- Ensure all environment variables and secrets are securely managed using Google Cloud best practices
- Follow security-first approach for all deployment steps
- Test Docker builds locally before pushing to GCR
